FBIS4-28144 "dreas110_c_94030" FBIS-EAS-94-110 Daily Report 6 Jun 1994 North Korea Kim Il-song's Reminiscences Carried by Media Kim Il-song's Reminiscences Carried by Media SK0606063494 Pyongyang KCNA in English 0530 GMT 6 Jun 94 SK0606063494 Pyongyang KCNA English BFN [Text] Pyongyang, June 6 (KCNA) -- The great leader President Kim Il-song's reminiscences "With the Century" was carried by foreign media. The Russian paper VETERAN No. 16 carried "A Spring of Trials" from Vol. 2 of part 1 the anti-Japanese revolution of the reminiscences, the Nepalese paper MAJADUR KISSAN and the Chinese magazine the CALAXY No. 5 "The Home Base" and "The Battle of the Tongning County Town" from Vol. 3 of part 1 the anti-Japanese revolution. The Tunisian paper AL OUAHEDA printed a photograph of President Kim Il-song and introduced the composition and content of Vol. 4 of part 1 the anti-Japanese revolution.
